    <div class="lg:flex-grow md:w-1/2 lg:pl-24 md:pl-16 flex flex-col md:items-start md:text-left items-center text-center">
      <h1 class="title-font sm:text-4xl text-3xl mb-4 font-medium text-gray-900">CHILLFILTR速 provides a home for Indie Music.
      </h1>
      <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">My name is Krister Axel. I love organic music with a solid groove and honest lyrics. I am always open to hearing new songs for inclusion on <%= link_to "Cloud Radio", pages_radio_path, class: "hover:text-white bg-teal-300" %>, <a class="hover:text-white bg-teal-300" href="https://kskq.org" target="_blank">KSKQ</a>, or as a blog post.</p>
	  <p>Send us your music <a class="hover:text-white bg-teal-300" href="https://www.submithub.com/to/chillfiltr" target="_blank" title="Send music">on SubmitHub.</a><br/>
	  Hire me for your next <%= link_to "Webflow migration", pages_webflow_migration_path, class: "hover:text-white bg-teal-300" %>.</p>
